WEBVTT

00:00.862 --> 00:04.607
Three months ago, a Spanish museum sent a Goya painting to be cleaned.

00:06.769 --> 00:08.011
The painting has disappeared.

00:08.715 --> 00:12.742
He's a very bad man who wanted to fund violent worldwide revolution.

00:14.955 --> 00:16.197
Countless lives are at stake.

00:16.813 --> 00:18.735
And you would like me to find it.

00:18.933 --> 00:19.468
Precisely.

00:20.425 --> 00:22.239
What's in it for me as they say?

00:22.347 --> 00:23.899
Do it for Queen and country.

00:24.199 --> 00:24.715
No!

00:25.991 --> 00:29.541
Alright, Queen and country, travel and living expenses, reasonable overheads.

00:29.617 --> 00:29.805
Done.

00:33.486 --> 00:35.412
I am Lord Charlie Mortdecai.

